  "rationale": "The hero is the sole inverse bookend and the only accent carrier \u2014 the sanctioned display-title-over-media plus a media-over-media overlap (reused seed). From there surfaces alternate primary/panel to give a different narrative rhythm than the brief order: manifesto (ghost 'ABOUT', staggered split) \u2192 full-bleed gallery band with static counter + marginal caption \u2192 a panel MISSION using interlock/float-wrap+inset to break the grid \u2192 heritage timeline as a stat-block behind a giant '1941' ghost word \u2192 curator quote-with-portrait collage. Per the variety directive the Visit block is a panel COLLAGE (address/hours/map/Buy-tickets) rather than a plain split, with the map as counterweight; newsletter uses an underline form-field with an inline typographic submit link (no boxed input, no button); footer is a panel with slash-nav and socials as plain links. Every non-hero section stays accent-free to honour single-accent, and all inputs/CTAs are typographic links to respect no-buttons/no-boxed-inputs."
}
